public ChromosomeFitnessComparator(boolean ascending,
                                   boolean speciated)
Enables sorting of chromosomes in order of fitness. Ascending order if ascending is true, descending otherwise. Uses fitness adjusted for species fitness sharing if speciated is true, raw fitness otherwise.
